[assistant] Fixed the failure and amended the commit.
[assistant] 
[assistant] Cause:
[assistant] - The test added a plain `String` into the real session persistence context via `addProxy(...)`.
[assistant] - On session close, Hibernate expects entries in `proxiesByKey` to be `HibernateProxy` instances and casts them, causing the reported `ClassCastException`.
[assistant] 
[assistant] Fix:
[assistant] - The test now creates a dedicated `StatefulPersistenceContext` instance with the same session instead of mutating the session-owned persistence context:
[assistant]   - `new StatefulPersistenceContext(session)`
[assistant] 
[assistant] Updated commit:
[assistant] - `0fb6744011 Add StatefulPersistenceContext serialization coverage`
[assistant] 
[assistant] I did not run the Gradle test command. The unrelated unstaged files remain untouched.
